high_descs: Head rotate and walk near the countertop.
Pick the apple from the table.
Turn right and put the apple in the sink.
Rinse the apple well inside the sink.
Pick the apple again from the fridge.
Turn left and place the apple in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: To place the apple in the fridge.

high_descs: Go to the countertop where the microwave is.
Take the apple on the right side.
Move to where the sink is.
Place the apple in the sink. Turn on the faucet. Wait six seconds. Turn the faucet off. Take the apple.
Stand in front of the fridge.
Open the top doors of the fridge. Place the apple on the second level. Close the doors.
anns.task_desc: Find an apple, wash it and place it in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn around and go near the counter top.
Take the apple from the counter top.
Turn around and go near the sink.
Put the apple into the sink and washed it.
Take it out and go near the fridge.
Put the apple into the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Placed the apple into the fridge.
